{"id":["109248691957829504"],"username":["pj"],"acct":["pj@qoto.org"],"display_name":["PJ"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[true],"group":[false],"created_at":["2022-10-29"],"note":["<p>Retired <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/systemsengineering\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>systemsengineering<\/span><\/a> professional and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/organizationalchange\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>organizationalchange<\/span><\/a> coach with decades of experience in the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/military\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>military<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/aerospace\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>aerospace<\/span><\/a> domains.<\/p><p>WRT <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/STEM\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>STEM<\/span><\/a>, I'm primarily interested in the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Science\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Science<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Engineering\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Engineering<\/span><\/a> of <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Systems\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Systems<\/span><\/a>. My stance towards <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Technology\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Technology<\/span><\/a> is opportunistic (will use whatever works best for the occasion) and I consider <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Mathematics\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Mathematics<\/span><\/a> a necessary evil to get things done properly.<\/p><p>My experience with <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/computing\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>computing<\/span><\/a> technology starts in the late '70s on a room-sized IBM machine running FORTRAN programs from buckets full of punch cards, turned hard towards HPL BASIC on a much smaller HP 9825A \"fully algebraic desktop calculator\" with a miniature magnetic tape cassette where to store programs, and abruptly ended a few years later after a couple of months of \"peeking\" and \"poking\" in ASM on an even smaller ZX81 connected to a BW portable TV.<\/p><p>Even if I was reasonably good at programming the moment I got my first DOS/Windows PC to play with at work and surf on something called the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Internet\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Internet<\/span><\/a>, I fell in love with things like <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/writing\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>writing<\/span><\/a>, <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/drawing\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>drawing<\/span><\/a>, and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/exploring\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>exploring<\/span><\/a> new ideas, that could now be done much better and faster with this new gadget, so I soon decided that being a <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/user\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>user<\/span><\/a>, doing the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/design\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>design<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/testing\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>testing<\/span><\/a> while dealing with other <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/people\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>people<\/span><\/a> to define <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/product\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>product<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/process\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>process<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/requirements\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>requirements<\/span><\/a> is much more fun than the actual <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/development\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>development<\/span><\/a> of the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/software\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>software<\/span><\/a> product itself.<\/p><p>I'm very glad I found this Mastodon <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/community\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>community<\/span><\/a> where we can \"Question Others to Teach Ourselves\". Please feel free to ask questions and argue with anything I say. Be sure I'll be doing the same. Nothing is sacred. There are no stupid questions, just BS answers.<\/p><p>Stay safe and be nice to others.<\/p><p>PJ<\/p>"],"url":["https://qoto.org/@pj"],"avatar":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/109/248/691/957/829/504/original/ed07d1a1134af6bc.gif"],"avatar_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/109/248/691/957/829/504/static/ed07d1a1134af6bc.png"],"header":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/headers/109/248/691/957/829/504/original/144de1a458455051.jpg"],"header_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/headers/109/248/691/957/829/504/original/144de1a458455051.jpg"],"followers_count":[21],"following_count":[10],"statuses_count":[220],"fields":[{"name":"Listening:","value":"<a href=\"https://radioparadise.com/listen/channels\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://<\/span><span class=\"ellipsis\">radioparadise.com/listen/chann<\/span><span class=\"invisible\">els<\/span><\/a>"}],"emojis":[]}
